---
---

<section class="section-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-image photo-frame">
        <img src="/img/pic/Nivedita5.jpg" alt="Nivedita Mishra" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="about-content">
        <span class="label">Who am I?</span>
        <h2>Meet Nivedita Mishra</h2>
        <p>
          With over 12 years of experience in Talent Acquisition, I specialise in hiring top technical talent and helping organisations build strong, diverse teams across Europe, North America, and India. My background spans in-house recruitment, RPO and agency environments, giving me end-to-end expertise in recruitment strategies- from job analysis and job advertising to sourcing, candidate management, and stakeholder engagement.
        </p>
        <div class="about-metrics">
          <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-value">12+</span>
            <span class="metric-label">Years in TA</span>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-value">3,000+</span>
            <span class="metric-label">Hires Made</span>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <span class="metric-value">16+</span>
            <span class="metric-label">Companies Served</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/about" class="btn btn-outline">Read Full Story</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-image {
    max-width: 350px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  @media (min-width: 769px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 350px 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }

  .about-content {
    min-width: 0;
    overflow-wrap: break-word;
    word-wrap: break-word;
  }

  .about-content .label {
    display: block;
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-content p {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-metrics {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }
</style>
